Titolo: Kuri Kinton

Anno: 1988

Descrizione: Kuri Kinton (功里金団) is a side-scrolling beat 'em up arcade game published by Taito. Players control a Chinese policeman who must dispatch numerous enemies while progressing through the game's levels. The object of the game is to rescue a senior policeman and his daughter, both of whom have been kidnapped by a gang and spirited away to an underground hideout.
The game received a mixed response from games critics.



Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
